name: Uno Card Game
description:
Install the Game Table plugin and start playing with your friends!

Shuffle and draw cards, reveal hidden information, flip cards over to place on the pile. Detailed instructions coming soon!

https://www.figma.com/community/plugin/823704590502753234/Game-Table

Update June 15th 2020
• Replaced card fill with rasterized fills to improve play performance. Original gradient fills are preserved as styles. Swap to gradients from the Components page if you want to to preserve quality for scaling or exporting.
